claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A table listing influenza vaccines (trade name, manufacturer), presentation (volume and format), age indication, hemagglutinin content per dose (µg HA), route of administration, and mercury content. Entries include Fluad Quadrivalent, Flublok Quadrivalent (recombinant HA vaccine), and FluMist Quadrivalent. The image only provides dosage, presentation, and route information for Flublok Quadrivalent and other vaccines; it does not mention antigenic matching to WHO- or FDA-selected strains and therefore does not support the claim.
